# Get Online Teams Meeting

# Description

Retrieve an online meeting using the join meeting ID or join meeting URL.

# Project compatibility

Windows | Cross-platform

# Configuration

* 
* Get by - Retrieve the meeting by the join meeting ID or the join meeting URL. Both are available in the Outlook/Teams calendar invite. This field supports String type input.









* Online Meeting - Automatically generated output variable.
* Join Meeting ID - A unique ID used for joining the meeting. Automatically generated output variable.
* Join Meeting URL - The web address used to join the online meeting. Automatically generated output variable.
* Meeting ID - A unique identifier for the online meeting. Automatically generated output variable.
